data.description: Step into a world where timeless elegance meets contemporary comfort in this exquisite craftsman-style residence. Nestled within the serene enclave of Ridgeview tucked in Duncan Park, this home beckons with its seamless fusion of historic charm and modern sophistication. Adorned with built-in bookshelves and a quaint phone nook, this residence pays homage to its heritage while boasting a plethora of contemporary upgrades in the kitchen, bathrooms, laundry room, security system and outside where entertaining areas abound with a double carport for convenience. Explore three spacious bedrooms, each exuding warmth and tranquility, along with two meticulously upgraded bathrooms and a refined laundry room all accessible on one level. The owner's suite has tons of natural light and double closets for all of your storage needs. The heart of the home is a chef's kitchen, where culinary adventures await amidst sleek appliances that will convey and upgraded finishes. Entertain in style in the beautifully designed great room, featuring a captivating fireplace, built-in book case and ample space for gatherings. Discover additional versatility in the flex room/playroom and an updated bonus room upstairs, offering endless possibilities for work or leisure. Outside, a double lot nestled in a cul-de-sac creates a sense of seclusion and tranquility, offering a private oasis amidst the vibrant pulse of Spartanburg. Enjoy the convenience of being mere minutes from the enchanting Mary Black Rail Trail and the vibrant energy of Downtown Spartanburg. Home is being sold "as-is" but with consideration of credit provided for any repairs if necessary. Indulge in a lifestyle where every detail is thoughtfully curated, and every comfort is effortlessly realized. Welcome home to a harmonious blend of past and present, where memories are made and cherished for years to come.
